## Accessories (Additional Services)

### Redis

```yaml
# config/deploy.yml

accessories:
  redis:
    image: redis:7
    host: 192.168.1.4
    port: 6379
    volumes:
      - /var/lib/redis:/data
```

### Sidekiq Worker

```yaml
# config/deploy.yml

servers:
  worker:
    hosts:
      - 192.168.1.5
    cmd: bundle exec sidekiq
    env:
      RAILS_MAX_THREADS: 10
```

